                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity_115 fixes and improvements.&lt;br/&gt;
This addresses below points in sanity test_115. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Do not skip the test when OST is remote.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fail Test if ll_ost_io thread has not started.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fail Test if ll_os_io post count is less then equal to ll_ost_io pre count.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fail Test if the count of started thread more than thread_max.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
